message.content: cs.IT, cs.IT is the most likely category as the paper deals with information theory and channel coding. Other likely categories could be cs.DS (data structures and algorithms) as the paper discusses decoding algorithms, cs.LG (machine learning) as the paper uses the Central Limit Theorem, cs.SY (systems and control) as the paper deals with control of information flow, and cs.NI (networking and internet architecture) as the paper deals with communication channels.
